  <div class="note-body">

    <div class="p-name entry-title p-summary summary e-content">
      <p>Talking of <a href="https://puredata.info/downloads/filterview">[filterview]</a> (<a href="https://github.com/pd-projects/filterview">gh</a>), here‚Äôs the abstraction I made for it, incorporating stereo smooth filters and a nice mode switching UI made of a [hslider] hidden behind a bunch of canvases.</p>

<p><img class="u-photo" src="https://waterpigs.co.uk/img/screen-shot-2018-06-17-at-195041.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>Each canvas has a receive ID of $0- plus the symbol for the relevant filter mode, making the message sending for changing the colours easy.</p>


